---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>👀 Hi, I'm Cuong.</h1>
			<p>
				I'm a backend software engineer who is passionate about computer science, distributed systems, and open-source software. Whenever I learn something interesting—whether it's a JVM optimization, a distributed systems paper, or a design pattern—I like to dig into the details rather than simply memorizing the conclusions.
			</p>
			<p>
				This blog is my digital notebook. I'll use it to document what I learn, share technical deep dives, summarize books and research papers, and occasionally write about lessons I've learned from building production systems. My hope is that writing helps me think more clearly and that these notes are useful to others on the same journey.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
